document.title: NIMBioS Products: January 2009 – February 2021

author.organization: National Institute for Mathematical and Biological Synthesis (NIMBioS)

document.abstract:
Excel file listing all of the NIMBioS products from January 2009 – February 2021, including the following:

  • Journal publications
  • Presentations
  • Grant proposals
  • Education modules and materials
  • Book chapters
  • Books
  • Evaluation instruments
  • Dissertations
  • Public interviews on NIMBioS work
  • Audio video products
  • Data and research materials

field.name: comments
field.value: The PDF attached to this entry lists product categories, and the Excel file with full details can be downloaded below.
